leftfirewall=yes needs to be enabled in ipsec.conf
This calls the ${PREFIX}/usr/lib/_updown. 
When a client comes up or goes down the _updown is called 
with PLUTO_VERB=up-client when the client comes up and 
PLUTO_VERB=down-client when the client goes down

_updown is located in ${PREFIX}/usr/lib/ipsec/ folder



